FBIS4-15954 "drsov071_r_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-071 Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 Azerbaijan Aliyev Postpones Visit to Georgia Aliyev Postpones Visit to Georgia LD1304001294 Moscow INTERFAX in English 2101 GMT 12 Apr 94 LD1304001294 Moscow INTERFAX English BFN [Text] Azerbaijani President Geydar Aliyev has put off his visit to Tbilisi scheduled for April 12. An informed source close to the Azerbaijani president told Interfax that the postponement was due to the "sudden large-scale Armenian offensive in the zone of the Karabakh conflict."
